overview: Six years after the defeat of Qilby, and five years after that of Jiva, the Tofu Brotherhood is forced back into service as the Chaos of Ogrest threatens to overwhelm the Sadida Kingdom. Using the Eliatrope Dofus seems to be the only solution to protect the Sadida people, but a mysterious organization has stolen them and the Tofu Brotherhood must take them back in order to confront Ogrest...
